<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/886763-i-loved-a-gentleman-in-moscow-and-rules-of">I LOVED A Gentleman in Moscow and Rules of Civility. Anyone have recommendations for a book like these - beautifully written, preferably historical, leaves you feeling expansive and engaged in life?</a>
